</div></div><div style="margin-top: 20px; background-color: #white;                        color: black;                       margin-left: 20px;                        margin-right: 20px;"><div style="position: absolute;                          left: 20px;"><a accesskey="p" href="tool-brush.html">Prev</a></div><div style="position: absolute;                          right: 20px;"><a accesskey="n" href="tool-polystar.html">Next</a></div><div class="navCenter">Tools</div></div><div class="sect1" lang="en"><div class="titlepage"><div><div><h2 class="title" style="clear: both"><a name="tool-color-picker"></a>Color Picker <span class="inlinemediaobject"><img src="tool_color_picker.png"></span>
</h2></div></div></div><p>To set the foreground color, <span class="mousebutton">left</span> click on
a pixel. To set the background color, <span class="mousebutton">right</span> click on a pixel.
<span class="application">KolourPaint</span> will then return to the previously selected tool.</p></div><div style="background-color: #white; color: black;                  margin-top: 20px; margin-left: 20px;                  margin-right: 20px;"><div style="position: absolute; left: 20px;"><a accesskey="p" href="tool-brush.html">Prev</a></div><div style="position: absolute; right: 20px;"><a accesskey="n" href="tool-polystar.html">Next</a></div><div align="center"><a accesskey="h" href="index.html">Home</a></div></div><div style="background-color: #white;   color: black;         margin-left: 20px;   margin-right: 20px;"><div class="navLeft">
Brush
<span class="inlinemediaobject"><img src="tool_brush.png"></span>
 </div><div class="navRight"> Connected Lines and Polygon
<span class="inlinemediaobject"><img src="tool_polystar.png"></span>
</div><div class="navCenter"><a accesskey="u" href="tools-chapter.html">Up</a></div></div><br><br><div class="bannerBottom" style="background-image: url(bottom-middle.png);                                        background-repeat: x-repeat;                                         width: 100%;                                         height: 100px;                                         bottom:0px;"><div class="BannerBottomRight"><img src="bottom-right.png" style="margin: 0px" alt=""></div><div class="bannerBottomLeft"><img src="bottom-left.png" style="margin: 0px;" alt=""></div></div></body></html></FILENAME><FILENAME filename="tool-polystar.html"><html><head><title>Connected Lines and Polygon

</title><link rel="stylesheet" href="kde-default.css" type="text/css"><meta name="generator" content="DocBook XSL Stylesheets V1.67.2"><meta name="keywords" content="kolourpaint, kdegraphics"><link rel="start" href="index.html" title="The KolourPaint Handbook"><link rel="up" href="tools-chapter.html" title="Chapter 3. Tools"><link rel="prev" href="tool-color-picker.html" title="Color Picker 
"><link rel="next" href="tool-curve.html" title="Curve 
"><meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=utf-8"><meta name="GENERATOR" content="KDE XSL Stylesheet V1.13 using libxslt"></head><body bgcolor="white" text="black" link="#0000FF" vlink="#840084" alink="#0000FF"><div style="background-image: url(top-middle.png); width: 100%; height: 131px;"><div style="position: absolute;                      right: 0px;"><img src="top-right-konqueror.png" style="margin: 0px" alt=""></div><div style="position: absolute; left: 0px;"><img src="top-left.png" style="margin: 0px" alt=""></div><div style="position: absolute;                         top: 25px;                          right: 100px;                          text-align: right;                          font-size: xx-large;                          font-weight: bold;                          text-shadow: #fff 0px 0px 5px;                          color: #444">Connected Lines and Polygon
<span class="inlinemediaobject"><img src="tool_polystar.png"></span>
</div></div><div style="margin-top: 20px; background-color: #white;                        color: black;                       margin-left: 20px;                        margin-right: 20px;"><div style="position: absolute;                          left: 20px;"><a accesskey="p" href="tool-color-picker.html">Prev</a></div><div style="position: absolute;                          right: 20px;"><a accesskey="n" href="tool-curve.html">Next</a></div><div class="navCenter">Tools</div></div><div class="sect1" lang="en"><div class="titlepage"><div><div><h2 class="title" style="clear: both"><a name="tool-polystar"></a>Connected Lines and Polygon
<span class="inlinemediaobject"><img src="tool_polystar.png"></span>
</h2></div></div></div><p>Click and drag to draw connected lines. The polygon tool is used in
the same way, however, the start and end points are automatically connected
to form a polygon.</p><p>The <span class="mousebutton">left</span> mouse button draws in the foreground color. The <span class="mousebutton">right</span> mouse button draws in the
background color, and will also reverse the fill color for polygons.</p><p>You can <a href="tool-options.html" title="Common Tool Options">set the line width</a>. For
polygons, you can also <a href="tool-options.html" title="Common Tool Options">set the fill
style</a>.</p></div><div style="background-color: #white; color: black;                  margin-top: 20px; margin-left: 20px;                  margin-right: 20px;"><div style="position: absolute; left: 20px;"><a accesskey="p" href="tool-color-picker.html">Prev</a></div><div style="position: absolute; right: 20px;"><a accesskey="n" href="tool-curve.html">Next</a></div><div align="center"><a accesskey="h" href="index.html">Home</a></div></div><div style="background-color: #white;   color: black;         margin-left: 20px;   margin-right: 20px;"><div class="navLeft">Color Picker <span class="inlinemediaobject"><img src="tool_color_picker.png"></span>
 </div><div class="navRight"> Curve <span class="inlinemediaobject"><img src="tool_curve.png"></span>
</div><div class="navCenter"><a accesskey="u" href="tools-chapter.html">Up</a></div></div><br><br><div class="bannerBottom" style="background-image: url(bottom-middle.png);                                        background-repeat: x-repeat;                                         width: 100%;                                         height: 100px;                                         bottom:0px;"><div class="BannerBottomRight"><img src="bottom-right.png" style="margin: 0px" alt=""></div><div class="bannerBottomLeft"><img src="bottom-left.png" style="margin: 0px;" alt=""></div></div></body></html></FILENAME><FILENAME filename="tool-curve.html"><html><head><title>Curve 
</title><link rel="stylesheet" href="kde-default.css" type="text/css"><meta name="generator" content="DocBook XSL Stylesheets V1.67.2"><meta name="keywords" content="kolourpaint, kdegraphics"><link rel="start" href="index.html" title="The KolourPaint Handbook"><link rel="up" href="tools-chapter.html" title="Chapter 3. Tools"><link rel="prev" href="tool-polystar.html" title="Connected Lines and Polygon

"><link rel="next" href="tool-ellipse.html" title="Ellipse 
"><meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=utf-8"><meta name="GENERATOR" content="KDE XSL Stylesheet V1.13 using libxslt"></head><body bgcolor="white" text="black" link="#0000FF" vlink="#840084" alink="#0000FF"><div style="background-image: url(top-middle.png); width: 100%; height: 131px;"><div style="position: absolute;                      right: 0px;"><img src="top-right-konqueror.png" style="margin: 0px" alt=""></div><div style="position: absolute; left: 0px;"><img src="top-left.png" style="margin: 0px" alt=""></div><div style="position: absolute;                         top: 25px;                          right: 100px;                          text-align: right;                          font-size: xx-large;                          font-weight: bold;                          text-shadow: #fff 0px 0px 5px;                          color: #444">Curve <span class="inlinemediaobject"><img src="tool_curve.png"></span>
</div></div><div style="margin-top: 20px; background-color: #white;                        color: black;                       margin-left: 20px;                        margin-right: 20px;"><div style="position: absolute;                          left: 20px;"><a accesskey="p" href="tool-polystar.html">Prev</a></div><div style="position: absolute;                          right: 20px;"><a accesskey="n" href="tool-ellipse.html">Next</a></div><div class="navCenter">Tools</div></div><div class="sect1" lang="en"><div class="titlepage"><div><div><h2 class="title" style="clear: both"><a name="tool-curve"></a>Curve <span class="inlinemediaobject"><img src="tool_curve.png"></span>
</h2></div></div></div><p>Click and drag to draw a line - this sets the start and end
points. You can set up to two control points by dragging. To finish the
curve without using both or any control points, click the other mouse
button. The curve tool draws a Cubic Bezier.</p><p>The <span class="mousebutton">left</span> mouse button draws in the foreground color. The <span class="mousebutton">right</span> mouse button draws in the
background color.</p><p>You can also <a href="tool-options.html" title="Common Tool Options">set the line
width</a>.</p></div><div style="background-color: #white; color: black;                  margin-top: 20px; margin-left: 20px;                  margin-right: 20px;"><div style="position: absolute; left: 20px;"><a accesskey="p" href="tool-polystar.html">Prev</a></div><div style="position: absolute; right: 20px;"><a accesskey="n" href="tool-ellipse.html">Next</a></div><div align="center"><a accesskey="h" href="index.html">Home</a></div></div><div style="background-color: #white;   color: black;         margin-left: 20px;   margin-right: 20px;"><div class="navLeft">Connected Lines and Polygon
<span class="inlinemediaobject"><img src="tool_polystar.png"></span>
 </div><div class="navRight"> Ellipse <span class="inlinemediaobject"><img src="tool_ellipse.png"></span>
</div><div class="navCenter"><a accesskey="u" href="tools-chapter.html">Up</a></div></div><br><br><div class="bannerBottom" style="background-image: url(bottom-middle.png);                                        background-repeat: x-repeat;                                         width: 100%;                                         height: 100px;                                         bottom:0px;"><div class="BannerBottomRight"><img src="bottom-right.png" style="margin: 0px" alt=""></div><div class="bannerBottomLeft"><img src="bottom-left.png" style="margin: 0px;" alt=""></div></div></body></html></FILENAME><FILENAME filename="tool-ellipse.html"><html><head><title>Ellipse 
</title><link rel="stylesheet" href="kde-default.css" type="text/css"><meta name="generator" content="DocBook XSL Stylesheets V1.67.2"><meta name="keywords" content="kolourpaint, kdegraphics"><link rel="start" href="index.html" title="The KolourPaint Handbook"><link rel="up" href="tools-chapter.html" title="Chapter 3. Tools"><link rel="prev" href="tool-curve.html" title="Curve 
"><link rel="next" href="tool-erasers.html" title="Erasers"><meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=utf-8"><meta name="GENERATOR" content="KDE XSL Stylesheet V1.13 using libxslt"></head><body bgcolor="white" text="black" link="#0000FF" vlink="#840084" alink="#0000FF"><div style="background-image: url(top-middle.png); width: 100%; height: 131px;"><div style="position: absolute;                      right: 0px;"><img src="top-right-konqueror.png" style="margin: 0px" alt=""></div><div style="position: absolute; left: 0px;"><img src="top-left.png" style="margin: 0px" alt=""></div><div style="position: absolute;                         top: 25px;                          right: 100px;                          text-align: right;                          font-size: xx-large;                          font-weight: bold;                          text-shadow: #fff 0px 0px 5px;                          color: #444">Ellipse <span class="inlinemediaobject"><img src="tool_ellipse.png"></span>
</div></div><div style="margin-top: 20px; background-color: #white;                        color: black;                       margin-left: 20px;                        margin-right: 20px;"><div style="position: absolute;                          left: 20px;"><a accesskey="p" href="tool-curve.html">Prev</a></div><div style="position: absolute;                          right: 20px;"><a accesskey="n" href="tool-erasers.html">Next</a></div><div class="navCenter">Tools</div></div><div class="sect1" lang="en"><div class="titlepage"><div><div><h2 class="title" style="clear: both"><a name="tool-ellipse"></a>Ellipse <span class="inlinemediaobject"><img src="tool_ellipse.png"></span>
</h2></div></div></div><p>Click and drag to draw an ellipse.</p><p>The <span class="mousebutton">left</span> mouse button draws in the foreground color. The <span class="mousebutton">right</span> mouse button draws in the
background color, and will reverse the fill color.</p><p>You can also <a href="tool-options.html" title="Common Tool Options">set the line width and fill
style</a>.</p><p>For additional functionality, use the modifier keys:</p><div class="itemizedlist"><ul type="disc"><li><p>Hold <span><strong class="keycap">Shift</strong></span> and drag to draw a circle.</p></li><li><p>To draw an ellipse with a center point of your choice, hold <span><strong class="keycap">Ctrl</strong></span>,
click on the center point, and drag until the ellipse is the correct size
and shape.</p></li><li><p>To draw a circle with a center point of your choice, hold <span><strong class="keycap">Ctrl</strong></span> and
<span><strong class="keycap">Shift</strong></span>, click on the center point, and drag until the circle is the correct
size.</p></li></ul></div></div><div style="background-color: #white; color: black;                  margin-top: 20px; margin-left: 20px;                  margin-right: 20px;"><div style="position: absolute; left: 20px;"><a accesskey="p" href="tool-curve.html">Prev</a></div><div style="position: absolute; right: 20px;"><a accesskey="n" href="tool-erasers.html">Next</a></div><div align="center"><a accesskey="h" href="index.html">Home</a></div></div><div style="background-color: #white;   color: black;         margin-left: 20px;   margin-right: 20px;"><div class="navLeft">Curve <span class="inlinemediaobject"><img src="tool_curve.png"></span>
 </div><div class="navRight"> Erasers</div><div class="navCenter"><a accesskey="u" href="tools-chapter.html">Up</a></div></div><br><br><div class="bannerBottom" style="background-image: url(bottom-middle.png);                                        background-repeat: x-repeat;                                         width: 100%;                                         height: 100px;                                         bottom:0px;"><div class="BannerBottomRight"><img src="bottom-right.png" style="margin: 0px" alt=""></div><div class="bannerBottomLeft"><img src="bottom-left.png" style="margin: 0px;" alt=""></div></div></body></html></FILENAME><FILENAME filename="tool-erasers.html"><html><head><title>Erasers</title><link rel="stylesheet" href="kde-default.css" type="text/css"><meta name="generator" content="DocBook XSL Stylesheets V1.67.2"><meta name="keywords" content="kolourpaint, kdegraphics"><link rel="start" href="index.html" title="The KolourPaint Handbook"><link rel="up" href="tools-chapter.html" title="Chapter 3. Tools"><link rel="prev" href="tool-ellipse.html" title="Ellipse 
"><link rel="next" href="tool-flood-fill.html" title="Flood Fill

"><meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=utf-8"><meta name="GENERATOR" content="KDE XSL Stylesheet V1.13 using libxslt"></head><body bgcolor="white" text="black" link="#0000FF" vlink="#840084" alink="#0000FF"><div style="background-image: url(top-middle.png); width: 100%; height: 131px;"><div style="position: absolute;                      right: 0px;"><img src="top-right-konqueror.png" style="margin: 0px" alt=""></div><div style="position: absolute; left: 0px;"><img src="top-left.png" style="margin: 0px" alt=""></div><div style="position: absolute;                         top: 25px;                          right: 100px;                          text-align: right;                          font-size: xx-large;                          font-weight: bold;                          text-shadow: #fff 0px 0px 5px;                          color: #444">Erasers</div></div><div style="margin-top: 20px; background-color: #white;                        color: black;                       margin-left: 20px;                        margin-right: 20px;"><div style="position: absolute;                          left: 20px;"><a accesskey="p" href="tool-ellipse.html">Prev</a></div><div style="position: absolute;                          right: 20px;"><a accesskey="n" href="tool-flood-fill.html">Next</a></div><div class="navCenter">Tools</div></div><div class="sect1" lang="en"><div class="titlepage"><div><div><h2 class="title" style="clear: both"><a name="tool-erasers"></a>Erasers</h2></div></div></div><div class="sect2" lang="en"><div class="titlepage"><div><div><h3 class="title"><a name="tool-eraser-std"></a>Eraser
<span class="inlinemediaobject"><img src="tool_eraser.png"></span>
</h3></div></div></div><p>Click and drag with the eraser to rub out mistakes.</p><div class="note" style="margin-left: 0.5in; margin-right: 0.5in;"><h3 class="title">Note</h3><p>Unlike other tools, the erasers draw in the background color. To draw
in the foreground color, use the <span class="mousebutton">right</span> mouse button.</p></div><p>The eraser only has <a href="tool-options.html" title="Common Tool Options">square
shapes</a>. To draw with other shapes such as circles use the <a href="tool-brush.html" title="
Brush

">Brush</a> and the <span class="mousebutton">right</span> mouse button.</p><div class="tip" style="margin-left: 0.5in; margin-right: 0.5in;"><h3 class="title">Tip</h3><p>Double-click on the Eraser icon to clear the entire image. This is
equivalent to using the <a href="image-clear.html" title="Clear">Clear</a> option on
the Image menu.</p></div></div><div class="sect2" lang="en"><div class="titlepage"><div><div><h3 class="title"><a name="tool-eraser-clr"></a>Color Eraser
<span class="inlinemediaobject"><img src="tool_color_washer.png"></span>
</h3></div></div></div><p>Click and drag to replace pixels of the foreground color with the
background color. To replace all pixels similar (but not necessarily exactly
equal) to the foreground color, such as in dithered images and photos, use a
<a href="working-with-color.html#color-box" title="The Color Box">Color Similarity</a> setting other than
Exact.</p><div class="note" style="margin-left: 0.5in; margin-right: 0.5in;"><h3 class="title">Note</h3><p>Unlike other tools, the erasers draw in the background color. To
replace pixels of the background color with the foreground color, use the
<span class="mousebutton">right</span> mouse button.</p></div><p>You can configure the <a href="tool-options.html" title="Common Tool Options">eraser
size</a>.</p><div class="tip" style="margin-left: 0.5in; margin-right: 0.5in;"><h3 class="title">Tip</h3><p>Double-click on the Color Eraser icon to apply it to the entire image.</p></div></div></div><div style="background-color: #white; color: black;                  margin-top: 20px; margin-left: 20px;                  margin-right: 20px;"><div style="position: absolute; left: 20px;"><a accesskey="p" href="tool-ellipse.html">Prev</a></div><div style="position: absolute; right: 20px;"><a accesskey="n" href="tool-flood-fill.html">Next</a></div><div align="center"><a accesskey="h" href="index.html">Home</a></div></div><div style="background-color: #white;   color: black;         margin-left: 20px;   margin-right: 20px;"><div class="navLeft">Ellipse <span class="inlinemediaobject"><img src="tool_ellipse.png"></span>
 </div><div class="navRight"> Flood Fill
<span class="inlinemediaobject"><img src="tool_flood_fill.png"></span>
</div><div class="navCenter"><a accesskey="u" href="tools-chapter.html">Up</a></div></div><br><br><div class="bannerBottom" style="background-image: url(bottom-middle.png);                                        background-repeat: x-repeat;                                         width: 100%;                                         height: 100px;                                         bottom:0px;"><div class="BannerBottomRight"><img src="bottom-right.png" style="margin: 0px" alt=""></div><div class="bannerBottomLeft"><img src="bottom-left.png" style="margin: 0px;" alt=""></div></div></body></html></FILENAME><FILENAME filename="tool-flood-fill.html"><html><head><title>Flood Fill

</title><link rel="stylesheet" href="kde-default.css" type="text/css"><meta name="generator" content="DocBook XSL Stylesheets V1.67.2"><meta name="keywords" content="kolourpaint, kdegraphics"><link rel="start" href="index.html" title="The KolourPaint Handbook"><link rel="up" href="tools-chapter.html" title="Chapter 3. Tools"><link rel="prev" href="tool-erasers.html" title="Erasers"><link rel="next" href="tool-line.html" title="
Line

"><meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=utf-8"><meta name="GENERATOR" content="KDE XSL Stylesheet V1.13 using libxslt"></head><body bgcolor="white" text="black" link="#0000FF" vlink="#840084" alink="#0000FF"><div style="background-image: url(top-middle.png); width: 100%; height: 131px;"><div style="position: absolute;                      right: 0px;"><img src="top-right-konqueror.png" style="margin: 0px" alt=""></div><div style="position: absolute; left: 0px;"><img src="top-left.png" style="margin: 0px" alt=""></div><div style="position: absolute;                         top: 25px;                          right: 100px;                          text-align: right;                          font-size: xx-large;                          font-weight: bold;                          text-shadow: #fff 0px 0px 5px;                          color: #444">Flood Fill
<span class="inlinemediaobject"><img src="tool_flood_fill.png"></span>
</div></div><div style="margin-top: 20px; background-color: #white;                        color: black;                       margin-left: 20px;                        margin-right: 20px;"><div style="position: absolute;                          left: 20px;"><a accesskey="p" href="tool-erasers.html">Prev</a></div><div style="position: absolute;                          right: 20px;"><a accesskey="n" href="tool-line.html">Next</a></div><div class="navCenter">Tools</div></div><div class="sect1" lang="en"><div class="titlepage"><div><div><h2 class="title" style="clear: both"><a name="tool-flood-fill"></a>Flood Fill
<span class="inlinemediaobject"><img src="tool_flood_fill.png"></span>
</h2></div></div></div><p>Click to fill a region. To fill a dithered region, use a <a href="working-with-color.html#color-box" title="The Color Box">Color Similarity</a> setting other than Exact.</p><p>The <span class="mousebutton">left</span> mouse button fills in the foreground color. The <span class="mousebutton">right</span> mouse button fills in the
background color.</p></div><div style="background-color: #white; color: black;                  margin-top: 20px; margin-left: 20px;                  margin-right: 20px;"><div style="position: absolute; left: 20px;"><a accesskey="p" href="tool-erasers.html">Prev</a></div><div style="position: absolute; right: 20px;"><a accesskey="n" href="tool-line.html">Next</a></div><div align="center"><a accesskey="h" href="index.html">Home</a></div></div><div style="background-color: #white;   color: black;         margin-left: 20px;   margin-right: 20px;"><div class="navLeft">Erasers </div><div class="navRight"> 
Line
<span class="inlinemediaobject"><img src="tool_line.png"></span>
