<span class="inlinemediaobject"><img src="tool_pen.png"></span>
</div></div><div style="margin-top: 20px; background-color: #white;                        color: black;                       margin-left: 20px;                        margin-right: 20px;"><div style="position: absolute;                          left: 20px;"><a accesskey="p" href="tool-line.html">Prev</a></div><div style="position: absolute;                          right: 20px;"><a accesskey="n" href="tool-rectangles.html">Next</a></div><div class="navCenter">Tools</div></div><div class="sect1" lang="en"><div class="titlepage"><div><div><h2 class="title" style="clear: both"><a name="tool-pen"></a>Pen
<span class="inlinemediaobject"><img src="tool_pen.png"></span>
</h2></div></div></div><p>Click to draw a dot or click and drag to draw a freehand line.</p><p>The <span class="mousebutton">left</span> mouse button draws in the foreground color. The <span class="mousebutton">right</span> mouse button draws in the
background color.  </p></div><div style="background-color: #white; color: black;                  margin-top: 20px; margin-left: 20px;                  margin-right: 20px;"><div style="position: absolute; left: 20px;"><a accesskey="p" href="tool-line.html">Prev</a></div><div style="position: absolute; right: 20px;"><a accesskey="n" href="tool-rectangles.html">Next</a></div><div align="center"><a accesskey="h" href="index.html">Home</a></div></div><div style="background-color: #white;   color: black;         margin-left: 20px;   margin-right: 20px;"><div class="navLeft">
Line
<span class="inlinemediaobject"><img src="tool_line.png"></span>
 </div><div class="navRight"> Rectangles
<span class="inlinemediaobject"><img src="tool_rectangles.png"></span>
</div><div class="navCenter"><a accesskey="u" href="tools-chapter.html">Up</a></div></div><br><br><div class="bannerBottom" style="background-image: url(bottom-middle.png);                                        background-repeat: x-repeat;                                         width: 100%;                                         height: 100px;                                         bottom:0px;"><div class="BannerBottomRight"><img src="bottom-right.png" style="margin: 0px" alt=""></div><div class="bannerBottomLeft"><img src="bottom-left.png" style="margin: 0px;" alt=""></div></div></body></html></FILENAME><FILENAME filename="tool-rectangles.html"><html><head><title>Rectangles

</title><link rel="stylesheet" href="kde-default.css" type="text/css"><meta name="generator" content="DocBook XSL Stylesheets V1.67.2"><meta name="keywords" content="kolourpaint, kdegraphics"><link rel="start" href="index.html" title="The KolourPaint Handbook"><link rel="up" href="tools-chapter.html" title="Chapter 3. Tools"><link rel="prev" href="tool-pen.html" title="Pen

"><link rel="next" href="tool-selections.html" title="Selections

"><meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=utf-8"><meta name="GENERATOR" content="KDE XSL Stylesheet V1.13 using libxslt"></head><body bgcolor="white" text="black" link="#0000FF" vlink="#840084" alink="#0000FF"><div style="background-image: url(top-middle.png); width: 100%; height: 131px;"><div style="position: absolute;                      right: 0px;"><img src="top-right-konqueror.png" style="margin: 0px" alt=""></div><div style="position: absolute; left: 0px;"><img src="top-left.png" style="margin: 0px" alt=""></div><div style="position: absolute;                         top: 25px;                          right: 100px;                          text-align: right;                          font-size: xx-large;                          font-weight: bold;                          text-shadow: #fff 0px 0px 5px;                          color: #444">Rectangles
<span class="inlinemediaobject"><img src="tool_rectangles.png"></span>
</div></div><div style="margin-top: 20px; background-color: #white;                        color: black;                       margin-left: 20px;                        margin-right: 20px;"><div style="position: absolute;                          left: 20px;"><a accesskey="p" href="tool-pen.html">Prev</a></div><div style="position: absolute;                          right: 20px;"><a accesskey="n" href="tool-selections.html">Next</a></div><div class="navCenter">Tools</div></div><div class="sect1" lang="en"><div class="titlepage"><div><div><h2 class="title" style="clear: both"><a name="tool-rectangles"></a>Rectangles
<span class="inlinemediaobject"><img src="tool_rectangles.png"></span>
</h2></div></div></div><p>Click and drag to draw a rectangle. The Rounded Rectangle is a Rectangle with rounded
corners.</p><p>The <span class="mousebutton">left</span> mouse button draws in the foreground color. The <span class="mousebutton">right</span> mouse button draws in the background color,
and will reverse the fill color.</p><p>You can also <a href="tool-options.html" title="Common Tool Options">set the line width and fill
style</a>.</p><p> For additional functionality, use the modifier keys:</p><div class="itemizedlist"><ul type="disc"><li><p>Hold <span><strong class="keycap">Shift</strong></span> and drag to draw a square.</p></li><li><p>To draw a rectangle with a center point of your choice, hold <span><strong class="keycap">Ctrl</strong></span>,
click on the center point, and drag until the rectangle is the correct size
and shape.</p></li><li><p>To draw a square with a center point of your choice, hold <span><strong class="keycap">Ctrl</strong></span> and <span><strong class="keycap">Shift</strong></span>,
click on the center point, and drag until the square is the correct size.</p></li></ul></div></div><div style="background-color: #white; color: black;                  margin-top: 20px; margin-left: 20px;                  margin-right: 20px;"><div style="position: absolute; left: 20px;"><a accesskey="p" href="tool-pen.html">Prev</a></div><div style="position: absolute; right: 20px;"><a accesskey="n" href="tool-selections.html">Next</a></div><div align="center"><a accesskey="h" href="index.html">Home</a></div></div><div style="background-color: #white;   color: black;         margin-left: 20px;   margin-right: 20px;"><div class="navLeft">Pen
<span class="inlinemediaobject"><img src="tool_pen.png"></span>
 </div><div class="navRight"> Selections
<span class="inlinemediaobject"><img src="tool_selections.png"></span>
</div><div class="navCenter"><a accesskey="u" href="tools-chapter.html">Up</a></div></div><br><br><div class="bannerBottom" style="background-image: url(bottom-middle.png);                                        background-repeat: x-repeat;                                         width: 100%;                                         height: 100px;                                         bottom:0px;"><div class="BannerBottomRight"><img src="bottom-right.png" style="margin: 0px" alt=""></div><div class="bannerBottomLeft"><img src="bottom-left.png" style="margin: 0px;" alt=""></div></div></body></html></FILENAME><FILENAME filename="tool-selections.html"><html><head><title>Selections

</title><link rel="stylesheet" href="kde-default.css" type="text/css"><meta name="generator" content="DocBook XSL Stylesheets V1.67.2"><meta name="keywords" content="kolourpaint, kdegraphics"><link rel="start" href="index.html" title="The KolourPaint Handbook"><link rel="up" href="tools-chapter.html" title="Chapter 3. Tools"><link rel="prev" href="tool-rectangles.html" title="Rectangles

"><link rel="next" href="tool-spraycan.html" title="Spraycan

"><meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=utf-8"><meta name="GENERATOR" content="KDE XSL Stylesheet V1.13 using libxslt"></head><body bgcolor="white" text="black" link="#0000FF" vlink="#840084" alink="#0000FF"><div style="background-image: url(top-middle.png); width: 100%; height: 131px;"><div style="position: absolute;                      right: 0px;"><img src="top-right-konqueror.png" style="margin: 0px" alt=""></div><div style="position: absolute; left: 0px;"><img src="top-left.png" style="margin: 0px" alt=""></div><div style="position: absolute;                         top: 25px;                          right: 100px;                          text-align: right;                          font-size: xx-large;                          font-weight: bold;                          text-shadow: #fff 0px 0px 5px;                          color: #444">Selections
<span class="inlinemediaobject"><img src="tool_selections.png"></span>
</div></div><div style="margin-top: 20px; background-color: #white;                        color: black;                       margin-left: 20px;                        margin-right: 20px;"><div style="position: absolute;                          left: 20px;"><a accesskey="p" href="tool-rectangles.html">Prev</a></div><div style="position: absolute;                          right: 20px;"><a accesskey="n" href="tool-spraycan.html">Next</a></div><div class="navCenter">Tools</div></div><div class="sect1" lang="en"><div class="titlepage"><div><div><h2 class="title" style="clear: both"><a name="tool-selections"></a>Selections
<span class="inlinemediaobject"><img src="tool_selections.png"></span>
</h2></div></div></div><p>Use the selection tools to draw out the boundary of a
selection.</p><p>You can click and drag on a selection to move it.</p><div class="tip" style="margin-left: 0.5in; margin-right: 0.5in;"><h3 class="title">Tip</h3><p>You can use the cursor keys while drawing out the boundary of the
selection or while moving it.</p></div><p>If you hold <span><strong class="keycap">Ctrl</strong></span> before moving the selection, then you will move a
copy of it. If you hold <span><strong class="keycap">Shift</strong></span> before moving the selection, you will smear
it.</p><div class="informaltable"><table border="1"><colgroup><col><col></colgroup><tbody><tr><td>
<span class="inlinemediaobject"><img src="selections_opaque_transparent.png"></span>
</td><td>
<p>There are two selection modes: Opaque (default) and Transparent. If
you use the Transparent selection mode, all pixels of the background color
will be transparent (background subtraction). This allows you to paste a
selection without the background. To perform background subtraction on a
dithered image, use a <a href="working-with-color.html#color-box" title="The Color Box">Color Similarity</a>
setting other than Exact.</p>
</td></tr></tbody></table></div><p>You can apply Image Effects to a selection - see the <a href="image-effects-chapter.html#image-effects-section" title="Image Effects Reference">Image Effects</a> section for more
information.</p></div><div style="background-color: #white; color: black;                  margin-top: 20px; margin-left: 20px;                  margin-right: 20px;"><div style="position: absolute; left: 20px;"><a accesskey="p" href="tool-rectangles.html">Prev</a></div><div style="position: absolute; right: 20px;"><a accesskey="n" href="tool-spraycan.html">Next</a></div><div align="center"><a accesskey="h" href="index.html">Home</a></div></div><div style="background-color: #white;   color: black;         margin-left: 20px;   margin-right: 20px;"><div class="navLeft">Rectangles
<span class="inlinemediaobject"><img src="tool_rectangles.png"></span>
 </div><div class="navRight"> Spraycan
<span class="inlinemediaobject"><img src="tool_spraycan.png"></span>
</div><div class="navCenter"><a accesskey="u" href="tools-chapter.html">Up</a></div></div><br><br><div class="bannerBottom" style="background-image: url(bottom-middle.png);                                        background-repeat: x-repeat;                                         width: 100%;                                         height: 100px;                                         bottom:0px;"><div class="BannerBottomRight"><img src="bottom-right.png" style="margin: 0px" alt=""></div><div class="bannerBottomLeft"><img src="bottom-left.png" style="margin: 0px;" alt=""></div></div></body></html></FILENAME><FILENAME filename="tool-spraycan.html"><html><head><title>Spraycan

</title><link rel="stylesheet" href="kde-default.css" type="text/css"><meta name="generator" content="DocBook XSL Stylesheets V1.67.2"><meta name="keywords" content="kolourpaint, kdegraphics"><link rel="start" href="index.html" title="The KolourPaint Handbook"><link rel="up" href="tools-chapter.html" title="Chapter 3. Tools"><link rel="prev" href="tool-selections.html" title="Selections

"><link rel="next" href="tool-text.html" title="Text

"><meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=utf-8"><meta name="GENERATOR" content="KDE XSL Stylesheet V1.13 using libxslt"></head><body bgcolor="white" text="black" link="#0000FF" vlink="#840084" alink="#0000FF"><div style="background-image: url(top-middle.png); width: 100%; height: 131px;"><div style="position: absolute;                      right: 0px;"><img src="top-right-konqueror.png" style="margin: 0px" alt=""></div><div style="position: absolute; left: 0px;"><img src="top-left.png" style="margin: 0px" alt=""></div><div style="position: absolute;                         top: 25px;                          right: 100px;                          text-align: right;                          font-size: xx-large;                          font-weight: bold;                          text-shadow: #fff 0px 0px 5px;                          color: #444">Spraycan
<span class="inlinemediaobject"><img src="tool_spraycan.png"></span>
</div></div><div style="margin-top: 20px; background-color: #white;                        color: black;                       margin-left: 20px;                        margin-right: 20px;"><div style="position: absolute;                          left: 20px;"><a accesskey="p" href="tool-selections.html">Prev</a></div><div style="position: absolute;                          right: 20px;"><a accesskey="n" href="tool-text.html">Next</a></div><div class="navCenter">Tools</div></div><div class="sect1" lang="en"><div class="titlepage"><div><div><h2 class="title" style="clear: both"><a name="tool-spraycan"></a>Spraycan
<span class="inlinemediaobject"><img src="tool_spraycan.png"></span>
</h2></div></div></div><p>Click and drag to spray graffiti. Hold down the mouse button for a
more concentrated spray.</p><div class="informaltable"><table border="1"><colgroup><col><col></colgroup><tbody><tr><td>
<span class="inlinemediaobject"><img src="spraycan_patterns.png"></span>
</td><td>
<p>Click on one of the shapes to select the spray size. You can select
from spray sizes of 9x9, 17x17 and 29x29.</p>
</td></tr></tbody></table></div><p>The <span class="mousebutton">left</span> mouse button draws in the foreground color. The <span class="mousebutton">right</span> mouse button draws in the
background color.</p></div><div style="background-color: #white; color: black;                  margin-top: 20px; margin-left: 20px;                  margin-right: 20px;"><div style="position: absolute; left: 20px;"><a accesskey="p" href="tool-selections.html">Prev</a></div><div style="position: absolute; right: 20px;"><a accesskey="n" href="tool-text.html">Next</a></div><div align="center"><a accesskey="h" href="index.html">Home</a></div></div><div style="background-color: #white;   color: black;         margin-left: 20px;   margin-right: 20px;"><div class="navLeft">Selections
<span class="inlinemediaobject"><img src="tool_selections.png"></span>
 </div><div class="navRight"> Text
<span class="inlinemediaobject"><img src="tool_text.png"></span>
</div><div class="navCenter"><a accesskey="u" href="tools-chapter.html">Up</a></div></div><br><br><div class="bannerBottom" style="background-image: url(bottom-middle.png);                                        background-repeat: x-repeat;                                         width: 100%;                                         height: 100px;                                         bottom:0px;"><div class="BannerBottomRight"><img src="bottom-right.png" style="margin: 0px" alt=""></div><div class="bannerBottomLeft"><img src="bottom-left.png" style="margin: 0px;" alt=""></div></div></body></html></FILENAME><FILENAME filename="tool-text.html"><html><head><title>Text

</title><link rel="stylesheet" href="kde-default.css" type="text/css"><meta name="generator" content="DocBook XSL Stylesheets V1.67.2"><meta name="keywords" content="kolourpaint, kdegraphics"><link rel="start" href="index.html" title="The KolourPaint Handbook"><link rel="up" href="tools-chapter.html" title="Chapter 3. Tools"><link rel="prev" href="tool-spraycan.html" title="Spraycan

"><link rel="next" href="tool-options.html" title="Common Tool Options"><meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=utf-8"><meta name="GENERATOR" content="KDE XSL Stylesheet V1.13 using libxslt"></head><body bgcolor="white" text="black" link="#0000FF" vlink="#840084" alink="#0000FF"><div style="background-image: url(top-middle.png); width: 100%; height: 131px;"><div style="position: absolute;                      right: 0px;"><img src="top-right-konqueror.png" style="margin: 0px" alt=""></div><div style="position: absolute; left: 0px;"><img src="top-left.png" style="margin: 0px" alt=""></div><div style="position: absolute;                         top: 25px;                          right: 100px;                          text-align: right;                          font-size: xx-large;                          font-weight: bold;                          text-shadow: #fff 0px 0px 5px;                          color: #444">Text
<span class="inlinemediaobject"><img src="tool_text.png"></span>
</div></div><div style="margin-top: 20px; background-color: #white;                        color: black;                       margin-left: 20px;                        margin-right: 20px;"><div style="position: absolute;                          left: 20px;"><a accesskey="p" href="tool-spraycan.html">Prev</a></div><div style="position: absolute;                          right: 20px;"><a accesskey="n" href="tool-options.html">Next</a></div><div class="navCenter">Tools</div></div><div class="sect1" lang="en"><div class="titlepage"><div><div><h2 class="title" style="clear: both"><a name="tool-text"></a>Text
<span class="inlinemediaobject"><img src="tool_text.png"></span>
</h2></div></div></div><p>
Click and drag an area in which to write text. Click and drag
on the border to move it. You can resize the text box by dragging on the
handles or by using the <a href="image-resize-scale.html" title="Resize / Scale">Resize</a> dialog.
</p><div class="tip" style="margin-left: 0.5in; margin-right: 0.5in;"><h3 class="title">Tip</h3><p>If you have deselected a text box you can use Undo to edit the text
again.</p></div><div class="sect2" lang="en"><div class="titlepage"><div><div><h3 class="title"><a name="tool-text-transparent"></a>Using the Transparent Color</h3></div></div></div><p>
<span class="inlinemediaobject"><img src="fcc_std_text.png"></span>
</p><p>The left picture shows the example image. The right picture shows the addition of text
with opaque foreground and background colors.
</p><p>
<span class="inlinemediaobject"><img src="fcc_trans_text.png"></span>
</p><p>The left picture shows the addition of text with an opaque foreground
color and transparent background color.  The right picture shows the
addition of text with a transparent foreground color and opaque background
color.</p></div></div><div style="background-color: #white; color: black;                  margin-top: 20px; margin-left: 20px;                  margin-right: 20px;"><div style="position: absolute; left: 20px;"><a accesskey="p" href="tool-spraycan.html">Prev</a></div><div style="position: absolute; right: 20px;"><a accesskey="n" href="tool-options.html">Next</a></div><div align="center"><a accesskey="h" href="index.html">Home</a></div></div><div style="background-color: #white;   color: black;         margin-left: 20px;   margin-right: 20px;"><div class="navLeft">Spraycan
<span class="inlinemediaobject"><img src="tool_spraycan.png"></span>
 </div><div class="navRight"> Common Tool Options</div><div class="navCenter"><a accesskey="u" href="tools-chapter.html">Up</a></div></div><br><br><div class="bannerBottom" style="background-image: url(bottom-middle.png);                                        background-repeat: x-repeat;                                         width: 100%;                                         height: 100px;                                         bottom:0px;"><div class="BannerBottomRight"><img src="bottom-right.png" style="margin: 0px" alt=""></div><div class="bannerBottomLeft"><img src="bottom-left.png" style="margin: 0px;" alt=""></div></div></body></html></FILENAME><FILENAME filename="tool-options.html"><html><head><title>Common Tool Options</title><link rel="stylesheet" href="kde-default.css" type="text/css"><meta name="generator" content="DocBook XSL Stylesheets V1.67.2"><meta name="keywords" content="kolourpaint, kdegraphics"><link rel="start" href="index.html" title="The KolourPaint Handbook"><link rel="up" href="tools-chapter.html" title="Chapter 3. Tools"><link rel="prev" href="tool-text.html" title="Text

