<span class="inlinemediaobject"><img src="eraser_shapes.png"></span>
</td><td>
<p>Click on one of the squares to select the eraser size. You can select
from squares of side length 2, 3, 5, 9, 17 and 29 pixels.</p>

<p>The eraser size setting affects the <a href="tool-erasers.html" title="Erasers">Erasers</a>.</p>
</td></tr><tr><td>
<span class="inlinemediaobject"><img src="line_width.png"></span>
</td><td>
<p>Click on one of the lines to select the line width. You can select
from line widths of 1, 2, 3, 5 and 8 pixel(s).</p>

<p>The line width setting affects the <a href="tool-polystar.html" title="Connected Lines and Polygon

">Connected Lines</a>, <a href="tool-curve.html" title="Curve 
">Curve</a>, <a href="tool-ellipse.html" title="Ellipse 
">Ellipse</a>, <a href="tool-line.html" title="
Line

">Line</a>, <a href="tool-polystar.html" title="Connected Lines and Polygon

">Polygon</a>, <a href="tool-rectangles.html" title="Rectangles

">Rectangle</a> and <a href="tool-rectangles.html" title="Rectangles

">Rounded Rectangle</a> tools.  </p>
</td></tr><tr><td>
<span class="inlinemediaobject"><img src="fill_style.png"></span>
</td><td>
<p>Click on one of the rectangles to select the fill style. You can
