nvert.html" title="Invert">Invert</a></p><p><a href="image-reduce-colors.html" title="Reduce Colors">Reduce Colors</a></p><p><a href="image-grayscale.html" title="Reduce to Grayscale">Reduce to Grayscale</a></p><p><a href="image-monochrome.html" title="Reduce to Monochrome (Dithered)">Reduce to Monochrome (Dithered)</a></p><p><a href="image-resize-scale.html" title="Resize / Scale">Resize / Scale</a></p><p><a href="image-rotate.html" title="Rotate">Rotate</a></p><p><a href="image-set-as-image.html" title="Set as Image (Crop)">Set as Image (Crop)</a></p><p><a href="image-skew.html" title="Skew">Skew</a></p><p><a href="image-soften-sharpen.html" title="Soften &amp; Sharpen">Soften &amp; Sharpen</a></p><p><a href="image-more-effects.html" title="More Effects">More Effects</a></p><p><a href="image-notes.html" title="Notes">Notes</a></p></div><FILENAME filename="image-autocrop.html"><html><head><title>Autocrop / Remove Internal Border</title><link rel="stylesheet" href="kde-default.css" type="text/css"><meta name="generator" content="DocBook XSL Stylesheets V1.67.2"><meta name="keywords" content="kolourpaint, kdegraphics"><link rel="start" href="index.html" title="The KolourPaint Handbook"><link rel="up" href="image-effects-chapter.html" title="Chapter 5. Image Effects"><link rel="prev" href="image-effects-chapter.html" title="Chapter 5. Image Effects"><link rel="next" href="image-balance.html" title="Balance"><meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=utf-8"><meta name="GENERATOR" content="KDE XSL Stylesheet V1.13 using libxslt"></head><body bgcolor="white" text="black" link="#0000FF" vlink="#840084" alink="#0000FF"><div style="background-image: url(top-middle.png); width: 100%; height: 131px;"><div style="position: absolute;                      right: 0px;"><img src="top-right-konqueror.png" style="margin: 0px" alt=""></div><div style="position: absolute; left: 0px;"><img src="top-left.png" style="margin: 0px" alt=""></div><div style="position: absolute;                         top: 25px;                          right: 100px;                          text-align: right;                          font-size: xx-large;                          font-weight: bold;                          text-shadow: #fff 0px 0px 5px;                          color: #444">Autocrop / Remove Internal Border</div></div><div style="margin-top: 20px; background-color: #white;                        color: black;                       margin-left: 20px;                        margin-right: 20px;"><div style="position: absolute;                          left: 20px;"><a accesskey="p" href="image-effects-chapter.html">Prev</a></div><div style="position: absolute;                          right: 20px;"><a accesskey="n" href="image-balance.html">Next</a></div><div class="navCenter">Image Effects</div></div><div class="sect1" lang="en"><div class="titlepage"><div><div><h2 class="title" style="clear: both"><a name="image-autocrop"></a>Autocrop / Remove Internal Border</h2></div></div></div><p>This automatically removes the border of an image or selection. Use
Autocrop if you have a figure that does not fill the entire image or selection and you
wish to remove the excess whitespace. To use this feature with a dithered
image border, you will also need to use <a href="working-with-color.html#color-box" title="The Color Box">Color
Similarity</a>.</p></div><div style="background-color: #white; color: black;                  margin-top: 20px; margin-left: 20px;                  margin-right: 20px;"><div style="position: absolute; left: 20px;"><a accesskey="p" href="image-effects-chapter.html">Prev</a></div><div style="position: absolute; right: 20px;"><a accesskey="n" href="image-balance.html">Next</a></div><div align="center"><a accesskey="h" href="index.html">Home</a></div></div><div style="background-color: #white;   color: black;         margin-left: 20px;   margin-right: 20px;"><div class="navLeft">Image Effects </div><div class="navRight"> Balance</div><div class="navCenter"><a accesskey="u" href="image-effects-chapter.html">Up</a></div></div><br><br><div class="bannerBottom" style="background-image: url(bottom-middle.png);                                        background-repeat: x-repeat;                                         width: 100%;                                         height: 100px;                                         bottom:0px;"><div class="BannerBottomRight"><img src="bottom-right.png" style="margin: 0px" alt=""></div><div class="bannerBottomLeft"><img src="bottom-left.png" style="margin: 0px;" alt=""></div></div></body></html></FILENAME><FILENAME filename="image-balance.html"><html><head><title>Balance</title><link rel="stylesheet" href="kde-default.css" type="text/css"><meta name="generator" content="DocBook XSL Stylesheets V1.67.2"><meta name="keywords" content="kolourpaint, kdegraphics"><link rel="start" href="index.html" title="The KolourPaint Handbook"><link rel="up" href="image-effects-chapter.html" title="Chapter 5. Image Effects"><link rel="prev" href="image-autocrop.html" title="Autocrop / Remove Internal Border"><link rel="next" href="image-clear.html" title="Clear"><meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=utf-8"><meta name="GENERATOR" content="KDE XSL Stylesheet V1.13 using libxslt"></head><body bgcolor="white" text="black" link="#0000FF" vlink="#840084" alink="#0000FF"><div style="background-image: url(top-middle.png); width: 100%; height: 131px;"><div style="position: absolute;                      right: 0px;"><img src="top-right-konqueror.png" style="margin: 0px" alt=""></div><div style="position: absolute; left: 0px;"><img src="top-left.png" style="margin: 0px" alt=""></div><div style="position: absolute;                         top: 25px;                          right: 100px;                          text-align: right;                          font-size: xx-large;                          font-weight: bold;                          text-shadow: #fff 0px 0px 5px;                          color: #444">Balance</div></div><div style="margin-top: 20px; background-color: #white;                        color: black;                       margin-left: 20px;                        margin-right: 20px;"><div style="position: absolute;                          left: 20px;"><a accesskey="p" href="image-autocrop.html">Prev</a></div><div style="position: absolute;                          right: 20px;"><a accesskey="n" href="image-clear.html">Next</a></div><div class="navCenter">Image Effects</div></div><div class="sect1" lang="en"><div class="titlepage"><div><div><h2 class="title" style="clear: both"><a name="image-balance"></a>Balance</h2></div></div></div><p>
This feature is accessible from the <a href="image-more-effects.html" title="More Effects">More Effects</a> dialog..
</p><p>
<span class="inlinemediaobject"><img src="image_balance.png"></span>
</p><p>This allows you to set the brightness, contrast and gamma of the image or selection.
</p><div class="note" style="margin-left: 0.5in; margin-right: 0.5in;"><h3 class="title">Note</h3><p>
The more common measure of gamma (a decimal from 0.10 to 10.00) is located between the
<span xmlns:doc="http://nwalsh.com/xsl/documentation/1.0" class="guiitem"><span class="guilabel">Gamma</span></span> spinbox and the <span xmlns:doc="http://nwalsh.com/xsl/documentation/1.0" class="guiitem"><span class="guibutton">Reset</span></span> button.
</p></div></div><div style="background-color: #white; color: black;                  margin-top: 20px; margin-left: 20px;                  margin-right: 20px;"><div style="position: absolute; left: 20px;"><a accesskey="p" href="image-autocrop.html">Prev</a></div><div style="position: absolute; right: 20px;"><a accesskey="n" href="image-clear.html">Next</a></div><div align="center"><a accesskey="h" href="index.html">Home</a></div></div><div style="background-color: #white;   color: black;         margin-left: 20px;   margin-right: 20px;"><div class="navLeft">Autocrop / Remove Internal Border </div><div class="navRight"> Clear</div><div class="navCenter"><a accesskey="u" href="image-effects-chapter.html">Up</a></div></div><br><br><div class="bannerBottom" style="background-image: url(bottom-middle.png);                                        background-repeat: x-repeat;                                         width: 100%;                                         height: 100px;                                         bottom:0px;"><div class="BannerBottomRight"><img src="bottom-right.png" style="margin: 0px" alt=""></div><div class="bannerBottomLeft"><img src="bottom-left.png" style="margin: 0px;" alt=""></div></div></body></html></FILENAME><FILENAME filename="image-clear.html"><html><head><title>Clear</title><link rel="stylesheet" href="kde-default.css" type="text/css"><meta name="generator" content="DocBook XSL Stylesheets V1.67.2"><meta name="keywords" content="kolourpaint, kdegraphics"><link rel="start" href="index.html" title="The KolourPaint Handbook"><link rel="up" href="image-effects-chapter.html" title="Chapter 5. Image Effects"><link rel="prev" href="image-balance.html" title="Balance"><link rel="next" href="image-emboss.html" title="Emboss"><meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=utf-8"><meta name="GENERATOR" content="KDE XSL Stylesheet V1.13 using libxslt"></head><body bgcolor="white" text="black" link="#0000FF" vlink="#840084" alink="#0000FF"><div style="background-image: url(top-middle.png); width: 100%; height: 131px;"><div style="position: absolute;                      right: 0px;"><img src="top-right-konqueror.png" style="margin: 0px" alt=""></div><div style="position: absolute; left: 0px;"><img src="top-left.png" style="margin: 0px" alt=""></div><div style="position: absolute;                         top: 25px;                          right: 100px;                          text-align: right;                          font-size: xx-large;                          font-weight: bold;                          text-shadow: #fff 0px 0px 5px;                          color: #444">Clear</div></div><div style="margin-top: 20px; background-color: #white;                        color: black;                       margin-left: 20px;                        margin-right: 20px;"><div style="position: absolute;                          left: 20px;"><a accesskey="p" href="image-balance.html">Prev</a></div><div style="position: absolute;                          right: 20px;"><a accesskey="n" href="image-emboss.html">Next</a></div><div class="navCenter">Image Effects</div></div><div class="sect1" lang="en"><div class="titlepage"><div><div><h2 class="title" style="clear: both"><a name="image-clear"></a>Clear</h2></div></div></div><p>This fills the entire image or selection with the background
color.</p><div class="tip" style="margin-left: 0.5in; margin-right: 0.5in;"><h3 class="title">Tip</h3><p>Double-click on the <a href="tool-erasers.html#tool-eraser-std" title="Eraser

">Eraser</a>
icon to clear the entire image.</p></div></div><div style="background-color: #white; color: black;                  margin-top: 20px; margin-left: 20px;                  margin-right: 20px;"><div style="position: absolute; left: 20px;"><a accesskey="p" href="image-balance.html">Prev</a></div><div style="position: absolute; right: 20px;"><a accesskey="n" href="image-emboss.html">Next</a></div><div align="center"><a accesskey="h" href="index.html">Home</a></div></div><div style="background-color: #white;   color: black;         margin-left: 20px;   margin-right: 20px;"><div class="navLeft">Balance </div><div class="navRight"> Emboss</div><div class="navCenter"><a accesskey="u" href="image-effects-chapter.html">Up</a></div></div><br><br><div class="bannerBottom" style="background-image: url(bottom-middle.png);                                        background-repeat: x-repeat;                                         width: 100%;                                         height: 100px;                                         bottom:0px;"><div class="BannerBottomRight"><img src="bottom-right.png" style="margin: 0px" alt=""></div><div class="bannerBottomLeft"><img src="bottom-left.png" style="margin: 0px;" alt=""></div></div></body></html></FILENAME><FILENAME filename="image-emboss.html"><html><head><title>Emboss</title><link rel="stylesheet" href="kde-default.css" type="text/css"><meta name="generator" content="DocBook XSL Stylesheets V1.67.2"><meta name="keywords" content="kolourpaint, kdegraphics"><link rel="start" href="index.html" title="The KolourPaint Handbook"><link rel="up" href="image-effects-chapter.html" title="Chapter 5. Image Effects"><link rel="prev" href="image-clear.html" title="Clear"><link rel="next" href="image-flatten.html" title="Flatten"><meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=utf-8"><meta name="GENERATOR" content="KDE XSL Stylesheet V1.13 using libxslt"></head><body bgcolor="white" text="black" link="#0000FF" vlink="#840084" alink