This feature is accessible from the <a href="image-more-effects.html" title="More Effects">More Effects</a> dialog..
</p><p>
<span class="inlinemediaobject"><img src="image_emboss.png"></span>
</p><p>
Check <span xmlns:doc="http://nwalsh.com/xsl/documentation/1.0" class="guiitem"><span class="guilabel">Enable</span></span> to apply the Emboss effect. This emphasises the edges and gives the
image or selection an "engraved look".
</p></div><div style="background-color: #white; color: black;                  margin-top: 20px; margin-left: 20px;                  margin-right: 20px;"><div style="position: absolute; left: 20px;"><a accesskey="p" href="image-clear.html">Prev</a></div><div style="position: absolute; right: 20px;"><a accesskey="n" href="image-flatten.html">Next</a></div><div align="center"><a accesskey="h" href="index.html">Home</a></div></div><div style="background-color: #white;   color: black;         margin-left: 20px;   margin-right: 20px;"><div class="navLeft">Clear </div><div class="navRight"> Flatten</div><div class="navCenter"><a accesskey="u" href="image-effects-chapter.html">Up</a></div></div><br><br><div class="bannerBottom" style="background-image: url(bottom-middle.png);                                        background-repeat: x-repeat;                                         width: 100%;                                         height: 100px;                                         bottom:0px;"><div class="BannerBottomRight"><img src="bottom-right.png" style="margin: 0px" alt=""></div><div class="bannerBottomLeft"><img src="bottom-left.png" style="margin: 0px;" alt=""></div></div></body></html></FILENAME><FILENAME filename="image-flatten.html"><html><head><title>Flatten</title><link rel="stylesheet" href="kde-default.css" type="text/css"><meta name="generator" content="DocBook XSL Stylesheets V1.67.2"><meta name="keywords" content="kolourpaint, kdegraphics"><link rel="start" href="index.html" title="The KolourPaint Handbook"><link rel="up" href="image-effects-chapter.html" title="Chapter 5. Image Effects"><link rel="prev" href="image-emboss.html" title="Emboss"><link rel="next" href="image-flip.html" title="Flip"><meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=utf-8"><meta name="GENERATOR" content="KDE XSL Stylesheet V1.13 using libxslt"></head><body bgcolor="white" text="black" link="#0000FF" vlink="#840084" alink="#0000FF"><div style="background-image: url(top-middle.png); width: 100%; height: 131px;"><div style="position: absolute;                      right: 0px;"><img src="top-right-konqueror.png" style="margin: 0px" alt=""></div><div style="position: absolute; left: 0px;"><img src="top-left.png" style="margin: 0px" alt=""></div><div style="position: absolute;                         top: 25px;                          right: 100px;                          text-align: right;                          font-size: xx-large;                          font-weight: bold;                          text-shadow: #fff 0px 0px 5px;                          color: #444">Flatten</div></div><div style="margin-top: 20px; background-color: #white;                        color: black;                       margin-left: 20px;                        margin-right: 20px;"><div style="position: absolute;                          left: 20px;"><a accesskey="p" href="image-emboss.html">Prev</a></div><div style="position: absolute;                          right: 20px;"><a accesskey="n" href="image-flip.html">Next</a></div><div class="navCenter">Image Effects</div></div><div class="sect1" lang="en"><div class="titlepage"><div><div><h2 class="title" style="clear: both"><a name="image-flatten"></a>Flatten</h2></div></div></div><p>
This feature is accessible from the <a href="image-more-effects.html" title="More Effects">More Effects</a> dialog..
</p><p>
<span class="inlinemediaobject"><img src="image_flatten.png"></span>
</p><p>
This recolors the image with varying shades of the two selected colors.
</p></div><div style="background-color: #white; color: black;                  margin-top: 20px; margin-left: 20px;                  margin-right: 20px;"><div style="position: absolute; left: 20px;"><a accesskey="p" href="image-emboss.html">Prev</a></div><div style="position: absolute; right: 20px;"><a accesskey="n" href="image-flip.html">Next</a></div><div align="center"><a accesskey="h" href="index.html">Home</a></div></div><div style="background-color: #white;   color: black;         margin-left: 20px;   margin-right: 20px;"><div class="navLeft">Emboss </div><div class="navRight"> Flip</div><div class="navCenter"><a accesskey="u" href="image-effects-chapter.html">Up</a></div></div><br><br><div class="bannerBottom" style="background-image: url(bottom-middle.png);                                        background-repeat: x-repeat;                                         width: 100%;                                         height: 100px;                                         bottom:0px;"><div class="BannerBottomRight"><img src="bottom-right.png" style="margin: 0px" alt=""></div><div class="bannerBottomLeft"><img src="bottom-left.png" style="margin: 0px;" alt=""></div></div></body></html></FILENAME><FILENAME filename="image-flip.html"><html><head><title>Flip</title><link rel="stylesheet" href="kde-default.css" type="text/css"><meta name="generator" content="DocBook XSL Stylesheets V1.67.2"><meta name="keywords" content="kolourpaint, kdegraphics"><link rel="start" href="index.html" title="The KolourPaint Handbook"><link rel="up" href="image-effects-chapter.html" title="Chapter 5. Image Effects"><link rel="prev" href="image-flatten.html" title="Flatten"><link rel="next" href="image-invert.html" title="Invert"><meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=utf-8"><meta name="GENERATOR" content="KDE XSL Stylesheet V1.13 using libxslt"></head><body bgcolor="white" text="black" link="#0000FF" vlink="#840084" alink="#0000FF"><div style="background-image: url(top-middle.png); width: 100%; height: 131px;"><div style="position: absolute;                      right: 0px;"><img src="top-right-konqueror.png" style="margin: 0px" alt=""></div><div style="position: absolute; left: 0px;"><img src="top-left.png" style="margin: 0px" alt=""></div><div style="position: absolute;                         top: 25px;                          right: 100px;                          text-align: right;                          font-size: xx-large;                          font-weight: bold;                          text-shadow: #fff 0px 0px 5px;                          color: #444">Flip</div></div><div style="margin-top: 20px; background-color: #white;                        color: black;                       margin-left: 20px;                        margin-right: 20px;"><div style="position: absolute;                          left: 20px;"><a accesskey="p" href="image-flatten.html">Prev</a></div><div style="position: absolute;                          right: 20px;"><a accesskey="n" href="image-invert.html">Next</a></div><div class="navCenter">Image Effects</div></div><div class="sect1" lang="en"><div class="titlepage"><div><div><h2 class="title" style="clear: both"><a name="image-flip"></a>Flip</h2></div></div></div><p>
<span class="inlinemediaobject"><img src="image_flip.png"></span>
</p><p>This flips the entire image or selection horizontally or
vertically.</p></div><div style="background-color: #white; color: black;                  margin-top: 20px; margin-left: 20px;                  margin-right: 20px;"><div style="position: absolute; left: 20px;"><a accesskey="p" href="image-flatten.html">Prev</a></div><div style="position: absolute; right: 20px;"><a accesskey="n" href="image-invert.html">Next</a></div><div align="center"><a accesskey="h" href="index.html">Home</a></div></div><div style="background-color: #white;   color: black;         margin-left: 20px;   margin-right: 20px;"><div class="navLeft">Flatten </div><div class="navRight"> Invert</div><div class="navCenter"><a accesskey="u" href="image-effects-chapter.html">Up</a></div></div><br><br><div class="bannerBottom" style="background-image: url(bottom-middle.png);                                        background-repeat: x-repeat;                                         width: 100%;                                         height: 100px;                                         bottom:0px;"><div class="BannerBottomRight"><img src="bottom-right.png" style="margin: 0px" alt=""></div><div class="bannerBottomLeft"><img src="bottom-left.png" style="margin: 0px;" alt=""></div></div></body></html></FILENAME><FILENAME filename="image-invert.html"><html><head><title>Invert</title><link rel="stylesheet" href="kde-default.css" type="text/css"><meta name="generator" content="DocBook XSL Stylesheets V1.67.2"><meta name="keywords" content="kolourpaint, kdegraphics"><link rel="start" href="index.html" title="The KolourPaint Handbook"><link rel="up" href="image-effects-chapter.html" title="Chapter 5. Image Effects"><link rel="prev" href="image-flip.html" title="Flip"><link rel="next" href="image-reduce-colors.html" title="Reduce Colors"><meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=utf-8"><meta name="GENERATOR" content="KDE XSL Stylesheet V1.13 using libxslt"></head><body bgcolor="white" text="black" link="#0000FF" vlink="#840084" alink="#0000FF"><div style="background-image: url(top-middle.png); width: 100%; height: 131px;"><div style="position: absolute;                      right: 0px;"><img src="top-right-konqueror.png" style="margin: 0px" alt=""></div><div style="position: absolute; left: 0px;"><img src="top-left.png" style="margin: 0px" alt=""></div><div style="position: absolute;                         top: 25px;                          right: 100px;                          text-align: right;                          font-size: xx-large;                          font-weight: bold;                          text-shadow: #fff 0px 0px 5px;                          color: #444">Invert</div></div><div style="margin-top: 20px; background-color: #white;                        color: black;                       margin-left: 20px;                        margin-right: 20px;"><div style="position: absolute;                          left: 20px;"><a accesskey="p" href="image-flip.html">Prev</a></div><div style="position: absolute;                          right: 20px;"><a accesskey="n" href="image-reduce-colors.html">Next</a></div><div class="navCenter">Image Effects</div></div><div class="sect1" lang="en"><div class="titlepage"><div><div><h2 class="title" style="clear: both"><a name="image-invert"></a>Invert</h2></div></div></div><p>
This feature is accessible from the <a href="image-more-effects.html" title="More Effects">More Effects</a> dialog..
</p><p>
<span class="inlinemediaobject"><img src="image_invert.png"></span>
</p><p>This allows you to invert one or more RGB channels in the image or selection. Select <span xmlns:doc="http://nwalsh.com/xsl/documentation/1.0" class="guiitem"><span class="guilabel">All</span></span> to change a photo into a negative and vice versa. This generally looks quite funny.</p><div class="tip" style="margin-left: 0.5in; margin-right: 0.5in;"><h3 class="title">Tip</h3><p>To quickly invert all channels, you do not need to use this dialog. You can instead
access the <span xmlns:doc="http://nwalsh.com/xsl/documentation/1.0" class="guiitem"><span class="guimenuitem">Invert Colors</span></span> item in the <span xmlns:doc="http://nwalsh.com/xsl/documentation/1.0" class="guiitem"><span class="guimenu">Image</span></span> or
<span xmlns:doc="http://nwalsh.com/xsl/documentation/1.0" class="guiitem"><span class="guimenu">Selection</span></span> menu.
</p></div></div><div style="background-color: #white; color: black;                  margin-top: 20px; margin-left: 20px;                  margin-right: 20px;"><div style="position: absolute; left: 20px;"><a accesskey="p" href="image-flip.html">Prev</a></div><div style="position: absolute; right: 20px;"><a accesskey="n" href="image-reduce-colors.html">Next</a></div><div align="center"><a accesskey="h" href="index.html">Home</a></div></div><div style="background-color: #white;   color: black;         margin-left: 20px;   margin-right: 20px;"><div class="navLeft">Flip </div><div class="navRight"> Reduce Colors</div><div class="navCenter"><a accesskey="u" href="image-effects-chapter.html">Up</a></div></div><br><br><div class="bannerBottom" style="background-image: url(bottom-middle.png);                                        background-repeat: x-repeat;                                         width: 100%;                                         height: 100px;                                         bottom:0px;"><div class="BannerBottomRight"><img src="bottom-right.png" style="margin: 0px" alt=""></div><div class="bannerBottomLeft"><img src="bottom-left.png" style="margin: 0px;" alt=""></div></div></body></html></FILENAME><FILENAME filename="image-reduce-colors.html"><html><head><title>Reduce Colors</title><link rel="stylesheet" href="kde-default.css" type="text/css"><meta name="generator" content="DocBook XSL Stylesheets V1.67.2"><meta name="keywords" content="kolourpaint, kdegraphics"><link rel="start" href="index.html" title="The KolourPaint Handbook"><link rel="up" href="image-effects-chapter.html" title="Chapter 5. Image Effects"><link rel="prev" href="image-invert.html" title="Invert"><link rel="next" href="image-grayscale.html" title="Reduce to Grayscale"><meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=utf-8"><meta name="GENERATOR" content="KDE XSL Stylesheet V1.13 using libxslt"></head><body bgcolor="white" text="black" link="#0000FF" vlink="#840084" alink="#0000FF"><div style="background-image: url(top-middle.png); width: 100%; height: 131px;"><div style="position: absolute;                      right: 0px;"><img src="top-right-konqueror.png" style="margin: 0px" alt=""></div><div style="position: absolute; left: 0px;"><img src="top-left.png" style="margin: 0px" alt=""></div><div style="position: absolute;                         top: 25px;                          right: 100px;                          text-align: right;                          font-size: xx-large;                          font-weight: bold;                          text-shadow: #fff 0px 0px 5px;                          color: #444">Reduce Colors</div></div><div style="margin-top: 20px; background-color: #white;                        color: black;                       margin-left: 20px;                        margin-right: 20px;"><div style="position: absolute;                          left: 20px;"><a accesskey="p" href="image-invert.html">Prev</a></div><div style="position: absolute;                          right: 20px;"><a accesskey="n" href="image-grayscale.html">Next</a></div><div class="navCenter">Image Effects</div></div><div class="sect1" lang="en"><div class="titlepage"><div><div><h2 class="title" style="clear: both"><a name="image-reduce-colors"></a>Reduce Colors</h2></div></div></div><p>
This feature is accessible from the <a href="image-more-effects.html" title="More Effects">More Effects</a> dialog..
</p><p>
<span class="inlinemediaobject"><img src="image_reduce_colors.png"></span>
</p><p>
This reduces the number of colors used by the image or selection, with or without dithering. Dithering
generally provides better quality results, however, you may wish to disable it for artistic effects;
<span class="abbrev">e.g.</span> using <span xmlns:doc="http://nwalsh.com/xsl/documentation/1.0" class="guiitem"><span class="guilabel">Monochrome</span></span> instead of
<span xmlns:doc="http://nwalsh.com/xsl/documentation/1.0" class="guiitem"><span class="guilabel">Monochrome (Dithered)</span></span> gives a silhouette effect.
</p><div class="tip" style="margin-left: 0.5in; margin-right: 0.5in;"><h3 class="title">Tip</h3><p>For a quick, dithered monochrome image or selection, use the <a href="image-monochrome.html" title="Reduce to Monochrome (Dithered)">Reduce to Monochrome (Dithered)</a> item of the <span xmlns:doc="http://nwalsh.com/xsl/documentation/1.0" class="guiitem"><span class="guimenu">Image</span></span> or <span xmlns:doc="http://nwalsh.com/xsl/documentation/1.0" class="guiitem"><span class="guimenu">Selection</span></span> menu.
</p></div><div class="note" style="margin-left: 0.5in; margin-right: 0.5in;"><h3 class="title">Note</h3><p>
Changing the number of colors here has no effect on the color depth of the file format. If you want to
change the color depth, you should select it in the file saving dialogs. Note that, confusingly, changing
the color depth also changes the number of colors.
</p></div></div><div style="background-color: #white; color: black;                  margin-top: 20px; margin-left: 20px;                  margin-right: 20px;"><div style="position: absolute; left: 20px;"><a accesskey="p" href="image-invert.html">Prev</a></div><div style="position: absolute; right: 20px;"><a accesskey="n" href="image-grayscale.html">Next</a></div><div align="center"><a accesskey="h" href="index.html">Home</a></div></div><div style="background-color: #white;   color: black;         margin-left: 20px;   margin-right: 20px;"><div class="navLeft">Invert </div><div class="navRight"> Reduce to Grayscale</div><div class="navCenter"><a accesskey="u" href="image-effects-chapter.html">Up</a></div></div><br><br><div class="bannerBottom" style="background-image: url(bottom-middle.png);                                        background-repeat: x-repeat;                                         width: 100%;                                         height: 100px;                                         bottom:0px;"><div class="BannerBottomRight"><img src="bottom-right.png" style="margin: 0px" alt=""></div><div class="bannerBottomLeft"><img src="bottom-left.png" style="margin: 0px;" alt=""></div></div></body></html></FILENAME><FILENAME filename="image-grayscale.html"><html><head><title>Reduce to Grayscale</title><link rel="stylesheet" href="kde-default.css" type="text/css"><meta name="generator" content="DocBook XSL Stylesheets V1.67.2"><meta name="keywords" content="kolourpaint, kdegraphics"><link rel="start" href="index.html" title="The KolourPaint Handbook"><link rel="up" href="image-effects-chapter.html" title="Chapter 5. Image Effects"><link rel="prev" href="image-reduce-colors.html" title="Reduce Colors"><link rel="next" href="image-monochrome.html" title="Reduce to Monochrome (Dithered)"><meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=utf-8"><meta name="GENERATOR" content="KDE XSL Stylesheet V1.13 using libxslt"></head><body bgcolor="white" text="black" link="#0000FF" vlink="#840084" alink="#0000FF"><div style="background-image: url(top-middle.png); width: 100%; height: 131px;"><div style="position: absolute;                      right: 0px;"><img src="top-right-konqueror.png" style="margin: 0px" alt=""></div><div style="position: absolute; left: 0px;"><img src="top-left.png" style="margin: 0px" alt=""></div><div style="position: absolute;                         top: 25px;                          right: 100px;                          text-align: right;                          font-size: xx-large;                          font-weight: bold;                          text-shadow: #fff 0px 0px 5px;                          color: #444">Reduce to Grayscale</div></div><div style="margin-top: 20px; background-color: #white;                        color: black;                       margin-left: 20px;                        margin-right: 20px;"><div style="position: absolute;                          left: 20px;"><a accesskey="p" href="image-reduce-colors.html">Prev</a></div><div style="position: absolute;                          right: 20px;"><a accesskey="n" href="image-monochrome.html">Next</a></div><div class="navCenter">Image Effects</div></div><div class="sect1" lang="en"><div class="titlepage"><div><div><h2 class="title" style="clear: both"><a name="image-grayscale"></a>Reduce to Grayscale</h2></div></div></div><p> This reduces the entire image or selection to grayscale.</p></div><div style="background-color: #white; color: black;                  margin-top: 20px; margin-left: 20px;                  margin-right: 20px;"><div style="position: absolute; left: 20px;"><a accesskey="p" href="image-reduce-colors.html">Prev</a></div><div style="position: absolute; right: 20px;"><a accesskey="n" href="image-monochrome.html">Next</a></div><div align="center"><a accesskey="h" href="index.html">Home</a></div></div><div style="background-color: #white;   color: black;         margin-left: 20px;   margin-right: 20px;"><div class="navLeft">Reduce Colors </div><div class="navRight"> Reduce to Monochrome (Dithered)</div><div class="navCenter"><a accesskey="u" href="image-effects-chapter.html">Up</a></div></div><br><br><div class="bannerBottom" style="background-image: url(bottom-middle.png);                                        background-repeat: x-repeat;                                         width: 100%;                                         height: 100px;                                         bottom:0px;"><div class="BannerBottomRight"><img src="bottom-right.png" style="margin: 0px" alt=""></div><div class="bannerBottomLeft"><img src="bottom-left.png" style="margin: 0px;" alt=""></div></div></body></html></FILENAME><FILENAME filename="image-monochrome.html"><html><head><title>Reduce to Monochrome (Dithered)</title><link rel="stylesheet" href="kde-default.css" type="text/css"><meta name="generator" content="DocBook XSL Stylesheets V1.67.2"><meta name="keywords" content="kolourpaint, kdegraphics"><link rel="start" href="index.html" title="The KolourPaint Handbook"><link rel="up" href="image-effects-chapter.html" title="Chapter 5. Image Effects"><link rel="prev" href="image-grayscale.html" title="Reduce to Grayscale"><link rel="next" href="image-resize-scale.html" title="Resize / Scale"><meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=utf-8"><meta name="GENERATOR" content="KDE XSL Stylesheet V1.13 using libxslt"></head><body bgcolor="white" text="black" link="#0000FF" vlink="#840084" alink="#0000FF"><div style="background-image: url(top-middle.png); width: 100%; height: 131px;"><div style="position: absolute;                      right: 0px;"><img src="top-right-konqueror.png" style="margin: 0px" alt=""></div><div style="position: absolute; left: 0px;"><img src="top-left.png" style="margin: 0px" alt=""></div><div style="position: absolute;                         top: 25px;                          right: 100px;                          text-align: right;                          font-size: xx-large;                          font-weight: bold;                          text-shadow: #fff 0px 0px 5px;                          color: #444">Reduce to Monochrome (Dithered)</div></div><div style="margin-top: 20px; background-color: #white;                        color: black;                       margin-left: 20px;                        margin-right: 20px;"><div style="position: absolute;                          left: 20px;"><a accesskey="p" href="image-grayscale.html">Prev</a></div><div style="position: absolute;                          right: 20px;"><a accesskey="n" href="image-resize-scale.html">Next</a></div><div class="navCenter">Image Effects</div></div><div class="sect1" lang="en"><div class="titlepage"><div><div><h2 class="title" style="clear: both"><a name="image-monochrome"></a>Reduce to Monochrome (Dithered)</h2></div></div></div><p>This reduces the entire image or selection to black and white.</p><div class="tip" style="margin-left: 0.5in; margin-right: 0.5in;"><h3 class="title">Tip</h3><p>
If you do not want the image or selection to be dithered, use the <a href="image-reduce-colors.html" title="Reduce Colors">
Reduce Colors</a> dialog.
</p></div></div><div style="background-color: #white; color: black;                  margin-top: 20px; margin-left: 20px;                  margin-right: 20px;"><div style="position: absolute; left: 20px;"><a accesskey="p" href="image-grayscale.html">Prev</a></div><div style="position: absolute; right: 20px;"><a accesskey="n" href="image-resize-scale.html">Next</a></div><div align="center"><a accesskey="h" href="index.html">Home</a></div></div><div style="background-color: #white;   color: black;         margin-left: 20px;   margin-right: 20px;"><div class="navLeft">Reduce to Grayscale </div><div class="navRight"> Resize / Scale</div><div class="navCenter"><a accesskey="u" href="image-effects-chapter.html">Up</a></div></div><br><br><div class="bannerBottom" style="background-image: url(bottom-middle.png);                                        background-repeat: x-repeat;                                         width: 100%;                                         height: 100px;                                         bottom:0px;"><div class="BannerBottomRight"><img src="bottom-right.png" style="margin: 0px" alt=""></div><div class="bannerBottomLeft"><img src="bottom-left.png" style="margin: 0px;" alt=""></div></div></body></html></FILENAME><FILENAME filename="image-resize-scale.html"><html><head><title>Resize / Scale</title><link rel="stylesheet" href="kde-default.css" type="text/css"><meta name="generator" content="DocBook XSL Stylesheets V1.67.2"><meta name="keywords" content="kolourpaint, kdegraphics"><link rel="start" href="index.html" title="The KolourPaint Handbook"><link rel="up" href="image-effects-chapter.html" title="Chapter 5. Image Effects"><link rel="prev" href="image-monochrome.html" title="Reduce to Monochrome (Dithered)"><link rel="next" href="image-rotate.html" title="Rotate"><meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=utf-8"><meta name="GENERATOR" content="KDE XSL Stylesheet V1.13 using libxslt"></head><body bgcolor="white" text="black" link="#0000FF" vlink="#840084" alink="#0000FF"><div style="background-image: url(top-middle.png); width: 100%; height: 131px;"><div style="position: absolute;                      right: 0px;"><img src="top-right-konqueror.png" style="margin: 0px" alt=""></div><div style="position: absolute; left: 0px;"><img src="top-left.png" style="margin: 0px" alt=""></div><div style="position: absolute;                         top: 25px;                          right: 100px;                          text-align: right;                          font-size: xx-large;                          font-weight: bold;                          text-shadow: #fff 0px 0px 5px;                          color: #444">Resize / Scale</div></div><div style="margin-top: 20px; background-color: #white;                        color: black;                       margin-left: 20px;                        margin-right: 20px;"><div style="position: absolute;                          left: 20px;"><a accesskey="p" href="image-monochrome.html">Prev</a></div><div style="position: absolute;                          right: 20px;"><a accesskey="n" href="image-rotate.html">Next</a></div><div class="navCenter">Image Effects</div></div><div class="sect1" lang="en"><div class="titlepage"><div><div><h2 class="title" style="clear: both"><a name="image-resize-scale"></a>Resize / Scale</h2></div></div></div><p>
<span class="inlinemediaobject"><img src="image_resize_scale.png"></span>
</p><p>Resizing the image changes the dimensions of the image without
applying a transformation to the existing contents. Scaling the image will
stretch the existing contents to the new dimensions. <span xmlns:doc="http://nwalsh.com/xsl/documentation/1.0" class="guiitem"><span class="guibutton">Smooth Scale</span></span>
generally provides better quality results than Scaling, by blending neighbouring colors.</p><p>You can express the new dimensions in pixels, or as a percentage of
the original size. If you select <span xmlns:doc="http://nwalsh.com/xsl/documentation/1.0" class="guiitem"><span class="guilabel">Keep aspect ratio</span></span>, the
width and height will be scaled by the same percentage.</p><div class="tip" style="margin-left: 0.5in; margin-right: 0.5in;"><h3 class="title">Tip</h3><p>
You can also resize the image or selection by dragging on the handles.
</p></div><div class="note" style="margin-left: 0.5in; margin-right: 0.5in;"><h3 class="title">Note</h3><p>Only scaling is supported for selections, and only resizing is
supported for text boxes. See <a href="image-notes.html" title="Notes">Notes</a> for
additional details about applying these effects.</p></div></div><div style="background-color: #white; color: black;                  margin-top: 20px; margin-left: 20px;                  margin-right: 20px;"><div style="position: absolute; left: 20px;"><a accesskey="p" href="image-monochrome.html">Prev</a></div><div style="position: absolute; right: 20px;"><a accesskey="n" href="image-rotate.html">Next</a></div><div align="center"><a accesskey="h" href="index.html">Home</a></div></div><div style="background-color: #white;   color: black;         margin-left: 20px;   margin-right: 20px;"><div class="navLeft">Reduce to Monochrome (Dithered) </div><div class="navRight"> Rotate</div><div class="navCenter"><a accesskey="u" href="image-effects-chapter.html">Up</a></div></div><br><br><div class="bannerBottom" style="background-image: url(bottom-middle.png);                                        background-repeat: x-repeat;                                         width: 100%;                                         height: 100px;                                         bottom:0px;"><div class="BannerBottomRight"><img src="bottom-right.png" style="margin: 0px" alt=""></div><div class="bannerBottomLeft"><img src="bottom-left.png" style="margin: 0px;" alt=""></div></div></body></html></FILENAME><FILENAME filename="image-rotate.html"><html><head><title>Rotate</title><link rel="stylesheet" href="kde-default.css" type="text/css"><meta name="generator" content="DocBook XSL Stylesheets V1.67.2"><meta name="keywords" content="kolourpaint, kdegraphics"><link rel="start" href="index.html" title="The KolourPaint Handbook"><link rel="up" href="image-effects-chapter.html" title="Chapter 5. Image Effects"><link rel="prev" href="image-resize-scale.html" title="Resize / Scale"><link rel="next" href="image-set-as-image.html" title="Set as Image (Crop)"><meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=utf-8"><meta name="GENERATOR" content="KDE XSL Stylesheet V1.13 using libxslt"></head><body bgcolor="white" text="black" link="#0000FF" vlink="#840084" alink="#0000FF"><div style="background-image: url(top-middle.png); width: 100%; height: 131px;"><div style="position: absolute;                      right: 0px;"><img src="top-right-konqueror.png" style="margin: 0px" alt=""></div><div style="position: absolute; left: 0px;"><img src="top-left.png" style="margin: 0px" alt=""></div><div style="position: absolute;                         top: 25px;                          right: 100px;                          text-align: right;                          font-size: xx-large;                          font-weight: bold;                          text-shadow: #fff 0px 0px 5px;                          color: #444">Rotate</div></div><div style="margin-top: 20px; background-color: #white;                        color: black;                       margin-left: 20px;                        margin-right: 20px;"><div style="position: absolute;                          left: 20px;"><a accesskey="p" href="image-resize-scale.html">Prev</a></div><div style="position: absolute;                          right: 20px;"><a accesskey="n" href="image-set-as-image.html">Next</a></div><div class="navCenter">Image Effects</div></div><div class="sect1" lang="en"><div class="titlepage"><div><div><h2 class="title" style="clear: both"><a name="image-rotate"></a>Rotate</h2></div></div></div><p>
<span class="inlinemediaobject"><img src="image_rotate.png"></span>
</p><p>This rotates the image. You can specify the angle and direction of
rotation.</p><div class="tip" style="margin-left: 0.5in; margin-right: 0.5in;"><h3 class="title">Tip</h3><p>You can reverse the direction of rotation by specifying a negative
custom angle.</p></div><div class="note" style="margin-left: 0.5in; margin-right: 0.5in;"><h3 class="title">Note</h3><p>See <a href="image-notes.html" title="Notes">Notes</a> for details about
applying this effect to a selection.
</p></div></div><div style="background-color: #white; color: black;                  margin-top: 20px; margin-left: 20px;                  margin-right: 20px;"><div style="position: absolute; left: 20px;"><a accesskey="p" href="image-resize-scale.html">Prev</a></div><div style="position: absolute; right: 20px;"><a accesskey="n" href="image-set-as-image.html">Next</a></div><div align="center"><a accesskey="h" href="index.html">Home</a></div></div><div style="background-color: #white;   color: black;         margin-left: 20px;   margin-right: 20px;"><div class="navLeft">Resize / Scale </div><div class="navRight"> Set as Image (Crop)</div><div class="navCenter"><a accesskey="u" href="image-effects-chapter.html">Up</a></div></div><br><br><div class="bannerBottom" style="background-image: url(bottom-middle.png);                                        background-repeat: x-repeat;                                         width: 100%;                                         height: 100px;                                         bottom:0px;"><div class="BannerBottomRight"><img src="bottom-right.png" style="margin: 0px" alt=""></div><div class="bannerBottomLeft"><img src="bottom-left.png" style="margin: 0px;" alt=""></div></div></body></html></FILENAME><FILENAME filename="image-set-as-image.html"><html><head><title>Set as Image (Crop)</title><link rel="stylesheet" href="kde-default.css" type="text/css"><meta name="generator" content="DocBook XSL Stylesheets V1.67.2"><meta name="keywords" content="kolourpaint, kdegraphics"><link rel="start" href="index.html" title="The KolourPaint Handbook"><link rel="up" href="image-effects-chapter.html" title="Chapter 5. Image Effects"><link rel="prev" href="image-rotate.html" title="Rotate"><link rel="next" href="image-skew.html" title="Skew"><meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=utf-8"><meta name="GENERATOR" content="KDE XSL Stylesheet V1.13 using libxslt"></head><body bgcolor="white" text="black" link="#0000FF" vlink="#840084" alink="#0000FF"><div style="background-image: url(top-middle.png); width: 100%; height: 131px;"><div style="position: absolute;                      right: 0px;"><img src="top-right-konqueror.png" style="margin: 0px" alt=""></div><div style="position: absolute; left: 0px;"><img src="top-left.png" style="margin: 0px" alt=""></div><div style="position: absolute;                         top: 25px;                          right: 100px;                          text-align: right;                          font-size: xx-large;                          font-weight: bold;                          text-shadow: #fff 0px 0px 5px;                          color: #444">Set as Image (Crop)</div></div><div style="margin-top: 20px; background-color: #white;                        color: black;                       margin-left: 20px;                        margin-right: 20px;"><div style="position: absolute;                          left: 20px;"><a accesskey="p" href="image-rotate.html">Prev</a></div><div style="position: absolute;                          right: 20px;"><a accesskey="n" href="image-skew.html">Next</a></div><div class="navCenter">Image Effects</div></div><div class="sect1" lang="en"><div class="titlepage"><div><div><h2 class="title" style="clear: both"><a name="image-set-as-image"></a>Set as Image (Crop)</h2></div></div></div><p>This will set the selection as the image.</p><div class="note" style="margin-left: 0.5in; margin-right: 0.5in;"><h3 class="title">Note</h3><p>This is only available when you have an active selection.</p></div></div><div style="background-color: #white; color: black;                  margin-top: 20px; margin-left: 20px;                  margin-right: 20px;"><div style="position: absolute; left: 20px;"><a accesskey="p" href="image-rotate.html">Prev</a></div><div style="position: absolute; right: 20px;"><a accesskey="n" href="image-skew.html">Next</a></div><div align="center"><a accesskey="h" href="index.html">Home</a></div></div><div style="background-color: #white;   color: black;         margin-left: 20px;   margin-right: 20px;"><div class="navLeft">Rotate </div><div class="navRight"> Skew</div><div class="navCenter"><a accesskey="u" href="image-effects-chapter.html">Up</a></div></div><br><br><div class="bannerBottom" style="background-image: url(bottom-middle.png);                                        background-repeat: x-repeat;                                         width: 100%;                                         height: 100px;                                         bottom:0px;"><div class="BannerBottomRight"><img src="bottom-right.png" style="margin: 0px" alt=""></div><div class="bannerBottomLeft"><img src="bottom-left.png" style="margin: 0px;" alt=""></div></div></body></html></FILENAME><FILENAME filename="image-skew.html"><html><head><title>Skew</title><link rel="stylesheet" href="kde-default.css" type="text/css"><meta name="generator" content="DocBook XSL Stylesheets V1.67.2"><meta name="keywords" content="kolourpaint, kdegraphics"><link rel="start" href="index.html" title="The KolourPaint Handbook"><link rel="up" href="image-effects-chapter.html" title="Chapter 5. Image Effects"><link rel="prev" href="image-set-as-image.html" title="Set as Image (Crop)"><link rel="next" href="image-soften-sharpen.html" title="Soften &amp; Sharpen"><meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=utf-8"><meta name="GENERATOR" content="KDE XSL Stylesheet V1.13 using libxslt"></head><body bgcolor="white" text="black" link="#0000FF" vlink="#840084" alink="#0000FF"><div style="background-image: url(top-middle.png); width: 100%; height: 131px;"><div style="position: absolute;                      right: 0px;"><img src="top-right-konqueror.png" style="margin: 0px" alt=""></div><div style="position: absolute; left: 0px;"><img src="top-left.png" style="margin: 0px" alt=""></div><div style="position: absolute;                         top: 25px;                          right: 100px;                          text-align: right;                          font-size: xx-large;                          font-weight: bold;                          text-shadow: #fff 0px 0px 5px;                          color: #444">Skew</div></div><div style="margin-top: 20px; background-color: #white;                        color: black;                       margin-left: 20px;                        margin-right: 20px;"><div style="position: absolute;                          left: 20px;"><a accesskey="p" href="image-set-as-image.html">Prev</a></div><div style="position: absolute;                          right: 20px;"><a accesskey="n" href="image-soften-sharpen.html">Next</a></div><div class="navCenter">Image Effects</div></div><div class="sect1" lang="en"><div class="titlepage"><div><div><h2 class="title" style="clear: both"><a name="image-skew"></a>Skew</h2></div></div></div><p>
<span class="inlinemediaobject"><img src="image_skew.png"></span>
</p><p>This skews the entire image or selection horizontally and/or
vertically.</p><div class="note" style="margin-left: 0.5in; margin-right: 0.5in;"><h3 class="title">Note</h3><p>See <a href="image-notes.html" title="Notes">Notes</a> for details about
applying this effect to a selection.</p></div></div><div style="background-color: #white; color: black;                  margin-top: 20px; margin-left: 20px;                  margin-right: 20px;"><div style="position: absolute; left: 20px;"><a accesskey="p" href="image-set-as-image.html">Prev</a></div><div style="position: absolute; right: 20px;"><a accesskey="n" href="image-soften-sharpen.html">Next</a></div><div align="center"><a accesskey="h" href="index.html">Home</a></div></div><div style="background-color: #white;   color: black;         margin-left: 20px;   margin-right: 20px;"><div class="navLeft">Set as Image (Crop) </div><div class="navRight"> Soften &amp; Sharpen</div><div class="navCenter"><a accesskey="u" href="image-effects-chapter.html">Up</a></div></div><br><br><div class="bannerBottom" style="background-image: url(bottom-middle.png);                                        background-repeat: x-repeat;                                         width: 100%;                                         height: 100px;                                         bottom:0px;"><div class="BannerBottomRight"><img src="bottom-right.png" style="margin: 0px" alt=""></div><div class="bannerBottomLeft"><img src="bottom-left.png" style="margin: 0px;" alt=""></div></div></body></html></FILENAME><FILENAME filename="image-soften-sharpen.html"><html><head><title>Soften &amp; Sharpen</title><link rel="stylesheet" href="kde-default.css" type="text/css"><meta name="generator" content="DocBook XSL Stylesheets V1.67.2"><meta name="keywords" content="kolourpaint, kdegraphics"><link rel="start" href="index.html" title="The KolourPaint Handbook"><link rel="up" href="image-effects-chapter.html" title="Chapter 5. Image Effects"><link rel="prev" href="image-skew.html" title="Skew"><link rel="next" href="image-more-effects.html" title="More Effects"><meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=utf-8"><meta name="GENERATOR" content="KDE XSL Stylesheet V1.13 using libxslt"></head><body bgcolor="white" text="black" link="#0000FF" vlink="#840084" alink="#0000FF"><div style="background-image: url(top-middle.png); width: 100%; height: 131px;"><div style="position: absolute;                      right: 0px;"><img src="top-right-konqueror.png" style="margin: 0px" alt=""></div><div style="position: absolute; left: 0px;"><img src="top-left.png" style="margin: 0px" alt=""></div><div style="position: absolute;                         top: 25px;                          right: 100px;                          text-align: right;                          font-size: xx-large;                          font-weight: bold;                          text-shadow: #fff 0px 0px 5px;                          color: #444">Soften &amp; Sharpen</div></div><div style="margin-top: 20px; background-color: #white;                        color: black;                       margin-left: 20px;                        margin-right: 20px;"><div style="position: absolute;                          left: 20px;"><a accesskey="p" href="image-skew.html">Prev</a></div><div style="position: absolute;                          right: 20px;"><a accesskey="n" href="image-more-effects.html">Next</a></div><div class="navCenter">Image Effects</div></div><div class="sect1" lang="en"><div class="titlepage"><div><div><h2 class="title" style="clear: both"><a name="image-soften-sharpen"></a>Soften &amp; Sharpen</h2></div></div></div><p>
This feature is accessible from the <a href="image-more-effects.html" title="More Effects">More Effects</a> dialog..
</p><p>
<span class="inlinemediaobject"><img src="image_soften_sharpen.png"></span>
</p><p>
Use this effect to soften or sharpen the image.
</p></div><div style="background-color: #white; color: black;                  margin-top: 20px; margin-left: 20px;                  margin-right: 20px;"><div style="position: absolute; left: 20px;"><a accesskey="p" href="image-skew.html">Prev</a></div><div style="position: absolute; right: 20px;"><a accesskey="n" href="image-more-effects.html">Next</a></div><div align="center"><a accesskey="h" href="index.html">Home</a></div></div><div style="background-color: #white;   color: black;         margin-left: 20px;   margin-right: 20px;"><div class="navLeft">Skew </div><div class="navRight"> More Effects</div><div class="navCenter"><a accesskey="u" href="image-effects-chapter.html">Up</a></div></div><br><br><div class="bannerBottom" style="background-image: url(bottom-middle.png);                                        background-repeat: x-repeat;                                         width: 100%;                                         height: 100px;                                         bottom:0px;"><div class="BannerBottomRight"><img src="bottom-right.png" style="margin: 0px" alt=""></div><div class="bannerBottomLeft"><img src="bottom-left.png" style="margin: 0px;" alt=""></div></div></body></html></FILENAME><FILENAME filename="image-more-effects.html"><html><head><title>More Effects</title><link rel="stylesheet" href="kde-default.css" type="text/css"><meta name="generator" content="DocBook XSL Stylesheets V1.67.2"><meta name="keywords" content="kolourpaint, kdegraphics"><link rel="start" href="index.html" title="The KolourPaint Handbook"><link rel="up" href="image-effects-chapter.html" title="Chapter 5. Image Effects"><link rel="prev" href="image-soften-sharpen.html" title="Soften &amp; Sharpen"><link rel="next" href="image-notes.html" title="Notes"><meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=utf-8"><meta name="GENERATOR" content="KDE XSL Stylesheet V1.13 using libxslt"></head><body bgcolor="white" text="black" link="#0000FF" vlink="#840084" alink="#0000FF"><div style="background-image: url(top-middle.png); width: 100%; height: 131px;"><div style="position: absolute;                      right: 0px;"><img src="top-right-konqueror.png" style="margin: 0px" alt=""></div><div style="position: absolute; left: 0px;"><img src="top-left.png" style="margin: 0px" alt=""></div><div style="position: absolute;                         top: 25px;                          right: 100px;                          text-align: right;                          font-size: xx-large;                          font-weight: bold;                          text-shadow: #fff 0px 0px 5px;                          color: #444">More Effects</div></div><div style="margin-top: 20px; background-color: #white;                        color: black;                       margin-left: 20px;                        margin-right: 20px;"><div style="position: absolute;                          left: 20px;"><a accesskey="p" href="image-soften-sharpen.html">Prev</a></div><div style="position: absolute;                          right: 20px;"><a accesskey="n" href="image-notes.html">Next</a></div><div class="navCenter">Image Effects</div></div><div class="sect1" lang="en"><div class="titlepage"><div><div><h2 class="title" style="clear: both"><a name="image-more-effects"></a>More Effects</h2></div></div></div><p>
This dialog contains the <a href="image-balance.html" title="Balance">Balance</a>,
<a href="image-emboss.html" title="Emboss">Emboss</a>, <a href="image-flatten.html" title="Flatten">Flatten</a>,
<a href="image-invert.html" title="Invert">Invert</a>, <a href="image-reduce-colors.html" title="Reduce Colors">Reduce Colors</a>
and <a href="image-soften-sharpen.html" title="Soften &amp; Sharpen">Soften &amp; Sharpen</a> features.
</p></div><div style="background-color: #white; color: black;                  margin-top: 20px; margin-left: 20px;                  margin-right: 20px;"><div style="position: absolute; left: 20px;"><a accesskey="p" href="image-soften-sharpen.html">Prev</a></div><div style="position: absolute; right: 20px;"><a accesskey="n" href="image-notes.html">Next</a></div><div align="center"><a accesskey="h" href="index.html">Home</a></div></div><div style="background-color: #white;   color: black;         margin-left: 20px;   margin-right: 20px;"><div class="navLeft">Soften &amp; Sharpen </div><div class="navRight"> Notes</div><div class="navCenter"><a accesskey="u" href="image-effects-chapter.html">Up</a></div></div><br><br><div class="bannerBottom" style="background-image: url(bottom-middle.png);                                        background-repeat: x-repeat;                                         width: 100%;                                         height: 100px;                                         bottom:0px;"><div class="BannerBottomRight"><img src="bottom-right.png" style="margin: 0px" alt=""></div><div class="bannerBottomLeft"><img src="bottom-left.png" style="margin: 0px;" alt=""></div></div></body></html></FILENAME><FILENAME filename="image-notes.html"><html><head><title>Notes</title><link rel="stylesheet" href="kde-default.css" type="text/css"><meta name="generator" content="DocBook XSL Stylesheets V1.67.2"><meta name="keywords" content="kolourpaint, kdegraphics"><link rel="start" href="index.html" title="The KolourPaint Handbook"><link rel="up" href="image-effects-chapter.html" title="Chapter 5. Image Effects"><link rel="prev" href="image-more-effects.html" title="More Effects"><link rel="next" href="credits.html" title="Chapter 6. Credits and License"><meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=utf-8"><meta name="GENERATOR" content="KDE XSL Stylesheet V1.13 using libxslt"></head><body bgcolor="white" text="black" link="#0000FF" vlink="#840084" alink="#0000FF"><div style="background-image: url(top-middle.png); width: 100%; height: 131px;"><div style="position: absolute;                      right: 0px;"><img src="top-right-konqueror.png" style="margin: 0px" alt=""></div><div style="position: absolute; left: 0px;"><img src="top-left.png" style="margin: 0px" alt=""></div><div style="position: absolute;                         top: 25px;                          right: 100px;                          text-align: right;                          font-size: xx-large;                          font-weight: bold;                          text-shadow: #fff 0px 0px 5px;                          color: #444">Notes</div></div><div style="margin-top: 20px; background-color: #white;                        color: black;                       margin-left: 20px;                        margin-right: 20px;"><div style="position: absolute;                          left: 20px;"><a accesskey="p" href="image-more-effects.html">Prev</a></div><div style="position: absolute;                          right: 20px;"><a accesskey="n" href="credits.html">Next</a></div><div class="navCenter">Image Effects</div></div><div class="sect1" lang="en"><div class="titlepage"><div><div><h2 class="title" style="clear: both"><a name="image-notes"></a>Notes</h2></div></div></div><p><a href="image-resize-scale.html" title="Resize / Scale">Resizing / Scaling</a>, <a href="image-rotate.html" title="Rotate">Rotating</a> and <a href="image-skew.html" title="Skew">Skewing</a> may change the dimensions of the
image. You can view the new dimensions in the dialog.</p><p>If you apply these effects to an image, the image will be resized if
necessary. However, if you apply these effects to a selection, the image
will not be resized, even if the transformed selection does not fit.</p><p>
<span class="inlinemediaobject"><img src="rotate_image_30.png"></span>
</p><p>
The left image has been rotated 30 degrees clockwise to form the right image. <span class="application">KolourPaint</span> has
automatically enlarged the image to accommodate the larger contents.
</p><p>
<span class="inlinemediaobject"><img src="rotate_selection_30.png"></span>
</p><p>
The left <span class="emphasis"><em>selection</em></span> has been rotated 30 degrees clockwise to form the right
selection. The image size has remained the same, hence parts of the selection will not be visible
without <a href="image-resize-scale.html" title="Resize / Scale">Resizing</a> the <span class="emphasis"><em>image</em></span>.
